# go-pubsub

Internal pubsub mechanism implemented in Go.

## Running

- Clone this repo
- Run `go get`
- Run `go run *.go`

It will start on port 8000

## Try it!

You can use cURL or anything to perform HTTP GET request to `http://localhost:8000` with `payload` query:

`curl http://localhost:8000\?payload\=John`

You'll see the output on the stdout log.

